Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.63,0:01:58.63,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.21,0:02:04.23,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.82,0:02:10.53,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was called the Wizard King,\Nand he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.32,0:02:17.82,sign_3221_4_Clover_Kingdom_R,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Clover Kingdom Royal Capital
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.22,0:02:25.34,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Time has passed, and the title
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.82,0:02:28.25,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,of the Wizard King has been \Npassed down through generations.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.25,0:02:33.09,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The Wizard King commands the Magic Knights,\Nand they protect the kingdom together.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.69,0:02:40.38,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The Magic Knights are comprised\Nof nine squads of mages
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.38,0:02:43.94,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,that specialize in combat, all under \Nthe command of the Wizard King.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.27,0:02:51.73,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,This band of heroes protects \Nthe kingdom with their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.73,0:02:58.29,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,To become the Wizard King or a Magic Knight \Nis the aspiration of all in the Clover Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.68,0:03:25.43,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,750)}To the Royal Capital of the Clover Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.48,0:03:29.73,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Grey words can't make anything happen
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.73,0:03:32.48,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, yeah I know
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.48,0:03:37.65,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Wishing to fly freely across the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.65,0:03:39.74,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I dreamed it all my life
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.74,0:03:43.49,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Step by step I go, though \Nit's a doubtful world 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.49,0:03:45.54,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't care how much I fall
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.54,0:03:49.01,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Instinct is my guide, I never give up
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.01,0:03:55.38,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,To faraway future, I burst out running
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.38,0:04:00.55,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Go beyond even the unseen fears
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.55,0:04:05.92,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The vision I had, so I can be myself
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.92,0:04:11.18,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday I will write the next page
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.18,0:04:14.70,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,You are my hope
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.70,0:04:17.44,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Like that page from someday
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.44,0:04:19.78,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to meet you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.78,0:04:22.74,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I call this a miracle
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.62,0:04:35.98,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Nine hundred and ninety-five...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.42,0:04:39.63,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Nine hundred and ninety-six...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.51,0:04:43.05,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Nine hundred and ninety-seven...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.87,0:04:46.15,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Nine hundred and ninety-eight...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.91,0:04:49.05,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Nine hundred and ninety-nine...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.43,0:04:54.44,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,One thousand!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.98,0:05:01.18,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Now to down some moguro leaf juice!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.63,0:05:02.74,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.15,0:05:04.70,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,One more gulp!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.16,0:05:07.20,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.23,0:05:10.70,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You want some, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.27,0:05:15.33,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.75,0:05:25.82,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I got my grimoire.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.35,0:05:31.22,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna keep climbing up,\Neven if I don't have any magical powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.65,0:05:33.27,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I'm not done yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.27,0:05:34.22,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not even close!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.65,0:05:36.54,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,One thousand and one!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.23,0:05:42.23,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Yuno's been training, too! I can't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.23,0:05:44.74,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,One thousand and two!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.78,0:05:50.21,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Asta was training for the \NMagic Knights Entrance Exam,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.21,0:05:54.73,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,which was to be held in the royal capital \Nof the Clover Kingdom in six months.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.47,0:05:57.50,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,So was Yuno.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.07,0:06:05.55,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I should wrap up for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.10,0:06:10.55,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,No, just a little bit more.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.46,0:06:13.51,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he's also...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.86,0:06:16.77,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,One thousand and one!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.90,0:06:21.15,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,One thousand and two!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.03,0:06:28.20,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Each one's goal was to one day \Nbecome the Wizard King.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.20,0:06:34.43,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,One thousand, five hundred and... three!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.29,0:06:42.46,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I can understand Yuno...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.46,0:06:46.46,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,But are you really considering allowing \NAsta to take the exam, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.46,0:06:50.51,main,Tower,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he's saying he wants to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.53,0:06:54.64,main,Tower,0000,0000,0000,,And the ones I was counting on...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.62,0:06:58.64,flashback,Boy A,0000,0000,0000,,W-We can't do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.09,0:07:01.09,flashback,Boy B,0000,0000,0000,,We can't become Magic Knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.09,0:07:04.73,flashback,Boy A,0000,0000,0000,,If someone who was kicked out of \Nthe Magic Knights was that strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.73,0:07:06.51,flashback,Boy A,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.75,0:07:09.43,flashback,Both,0000,0000,0000,,We're sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.70,0:07:15.87,main,Tower,0000,0000,0000,,...decided against taking the exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.87,0:07:20.07,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Again, I believe Yuno will be fine, \Nbut I don't think Asta's up for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.07,0:07:24.14,main,Tower,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he's saying he wants to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.14,0:07:28.38,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Again{\i0}, I believe Yuno will be fine,\Nbut it'll be pointless for Asta to take them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.38,0:07:32.63,main,Tower,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he's saying he wants to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.31,0:07:38.71,main,Tower,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, the idea of Asta going to the royal\Ncapital just makes you feel lonely, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.26,0:07:40.60,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.91,0:07:42.65,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.65,0:07:45.90,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,I just believe that if he's \Ngoing to fail anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.90,0:07:48.16,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,he's better off not taking \Nit in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.16,0:07:51.38,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,A-And you know... The little \Nones will miss him, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.38,0:07:54.62,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Not me! But they'll have one \Nless person to play with!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.79,0:07:57.29,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you looking at me like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.38,0:07:59.91,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Not you, too, Tower Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.91,0:08:04.50,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll feel a little lonely with \Nboth Yuno and Asta gone, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.91,0:08:10.79,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Well, of course, I raised them, and I've lived \Nwith them ever since they were babies.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.79,0:08:13.26,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be lying if I said I wasn't \Na bit sad to see them go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.26,0:08:17.29,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,If possible, I'd like for them \Nto stay at the church.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.29,0:08:20.27,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,But I also want to let them \Ndo what they want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.27,0:08:22.14,main,Tower,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.14,0:08:25.03,main,Tower,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, you know... Yuno will be fine,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.03,0:08:28.77,main,Tower,0000,0000,0000,,and Asta might fail the exam \Nand come right back anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.77,0:08:32.41,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're right. Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.41,0:08:35.28,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno will be fine, but the \Nother one will come right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.11,0:08:40.22,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Um... The book that Asta obtained...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.67,0:08:43.55,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Is it truly a grimoire?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.55,0:08:46.92,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Asta can't use magic. How was \Nhe able to obtain a grimoire?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.23,0:08:48.23,main,Tower,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.41,0:08:51.27,main,Tower,0000,0000,0000,,But that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.27,0:08:52.34,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.70,0:08:53.73,main,Tower,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.89,0:08:57.05,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Look! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.05,0:08:59.06,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,My very own grimoire!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.06,0:09:02.77,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even know how,\N but I was able to get one!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.41,0:09:08.40,italics,Tower,0000,0000,0000,,The five-leaf clover... It couldn't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.73,0:09:15.15,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Training's not over until \NI'm back at the church!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.57,0:09:17.16,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Eat my dust!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.53,0:09:34.61,main,Rekka,0000,0000,0000,,Goal!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.61,0:09:36.54,main,Arlu,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno! Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.54,0:09:37.76,main,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.22,0:09:40.13,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Who got here faster?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.13,0:09:44.65,main,Nash,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... Yuno was just a tiny bit faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.65,0:09:47.02,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?! Were you even looking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.55,0:09:52.40,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll race you into the church!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.53,0:09:59.65,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I win.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.45,0:10:04.65,main,Rekka,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno can be pretty childish sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.65,0:10:07.96,main,Nash,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I mean, getting so worked \Nup over Asta, of all people?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.96,0:10:09.91,main,Nash,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention, Yuno...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.91,0:10:12.17,main,Nash,0000,0000,0000,,How many years will this last us?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.07,0:10:26.33,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the Wizard King.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.17,0:10:53.53,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.17,0:10:56.63,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Did you come to watch me train?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.14,0:10:58.19,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Nash?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.17,0:11:01.30,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.30,0:11:04.09,main,Nash,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing. I was just bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.09,0:11:07.51,main,Nash,0000,0000,0000,,I just came by to make fun of the \Nidiot doing something idiotic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.51,0:11:09.14,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Whaddya mean, idiotic?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.50,0:11:11.22,main,Nash,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.22,0:11:15.21,main,Nash,0000,0000,0000,,You can't even use magic, and you're going \Nto take the Magic Knights Entrance Exam?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.21,0:11:16.44,main,Nash,0000,0000,0000,,Of course you're going to fail!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.44,0:11:18.82,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That's not decided yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.70,0:11:21.03,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Just look!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.42,0:11:23.66,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I even got a grimoire!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.66,0:11:26.12,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna get into the Magic Knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.45,0:11:28.73,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,And then, one day, I'll become the Wizard Ki—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.73,0:11:29.98,main,Nash,0000,0000,0000,,That's never gonna happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.93,0:11:37.46,main,Nash,0000,0000,0000,,Orphans like us, who are poor... \Naren't allowed to dream like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.46,0:11:39.57,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Nash...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.97,0:11:48.53,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You can't give up right from the get-go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.53,0:11:50.85,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Possibilities exist in everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.85,0:11:53.79,main,Nash,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! They do not!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.79,0:11:56.69,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,No, they do! I'm going to \Nkeep chasing my dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.57,0:11:59.61,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter if you're \Npoor or an orphan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.61,0:12:02.01,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone in this world can become amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.01,0:12:03.85,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,They can do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.85,0:12:05.58,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,They can make their dreams come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.58,0:12:08.11,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,They can make everyone happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.06,0:12:11.00,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll prove that to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.00,0:12:12.72,main,Nash,0000,0000,0000,,Prove?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.72,0:12:14.62,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to join the Magic Knights
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.62,0:12:17.63,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,and become the Wizard King!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.15,0:12:44.02,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow's the day Asta and Yuno \Nset out for the royal capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.02,0:12:45.99,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,We have to send them off with a bang!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.99,0:12:51.33,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Father went to all the surrounding \Nvillages asking for tatoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.33,0:12:52.66,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.66,0:12:55.67,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,What's that look for?\NThis isn't just for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.67,0:12:58.54,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, it's mostly for Yuno.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.54,0:12:59.84,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.31,0:13:05.09,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you know... Yuno might make it \Ninto the Magic Knights, but you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.09,0:13:06.33,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.41,0:13:11.57,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Asta, there's no need to be embarrassed, \Neven if you fail the exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.57,0:13:12.41,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.11,0:13:15.62,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,No one believes you're going to pass, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.62,0:13:18.86,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to encourage \Nme or make fun of me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.21,0:13:21.61,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,You can come back at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.33,0:13:25.03,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Your home is this church.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.69,0:13:29.53,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how crappy or poor \Nit may be, it's your home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.53,0:13:31.65,main,Rekka,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.65,0:13:34.51,main,Arlu,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be lonely without Asta here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.51,0:13:35.82,main,Arlu,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.82,0:13:37.54,main,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,We're all family.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.54,0:13:40.45,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You should say that to Yuno, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.45,0:13:42.77,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Tell him he can come back\Nwhenever he wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.77,0:13:44.66,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.14,0:13:48.55,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?! Besides, I'll be fine, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.55,0:13:50.43,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the Wizard King!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.43,0:13:52.89,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,And then... I'm gonna come back for Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.37,0:13:55.23,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So when that happens, marry m—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.75,0:13:58.83,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.83,0:14:02.41,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,We have stewed tatoes,\Ntato tempura, grilled tatoes,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.41,0:14:05.73,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,fried tatoes, stir-fried \Ntatoes, steamed tatoes,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.73,0:14:10.79,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Hage-style boiled tatoes, tato juice, \Nand even special tato pudding!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.79,0:14:14.37,main,Arlu and horo,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.55,0:14:17.55,main,Arlu,0000,0000,0000,,So flaky and delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.55,0:14:18.62,main,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,Yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.62,0:14:20.09,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.09,0:14:22.96,main,Rekka,0000,0000,0000,,Don't eat it all yourself, Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.96,0:14:24.69,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So good!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.14,0:14:33.61,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.61,0:14:36.14,main,Rekka,0000,0000,0000,,You better write us, Yuno.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.14,0:14:37.18,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.53,0:14:40.02,main,Arlu,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.02,0:14:41.93,main,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,Come back soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.93,0:14:44.36,main,Nash,0000,0000,0000,,He'll be back soon... Asta, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.36,0:14:45.92,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Nash!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.92,0:14:46.85,main,Nash,0000,0000,0000,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.63,0:14:50.93,main,Nash,0000,0000,0000,,If, just if, and it's a very huge if...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.93,0:14:53.51,main,Nash,0000,0000,0000,,If you get into the Magic Knights...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.51,0:14:54.40,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.89,0:14:59.36,main,Nash,0000,0000,0000,,I'll believe in possibilities. \NI'll believe I can become anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.36,0:15:02.42,main,Nash,0000,0000,0000,,And then one day, I'll get into \Nthe Magic Knights, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.80,0:15:04.93,main,Nash,0000,0000,0000,,No, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.93,0:15:06.30,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.73,0:15:09.46,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll be off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.46,0:15:10.97,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait, Yuno!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.25,0:15:14.82,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me, you handsome jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.82,0:15:18.22,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Just because we're rivals doesn't \Nmean we can't get along!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.66,0:15:19.73,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.14,0:15:22.73,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Well, bye, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.12,0:15:25.85,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Have a safe trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.85,0:15:26.98,main,Nash,0000,0000,0000,,See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.49,0:15:35.15,italics,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno and Asta... You've both grown so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.93,0:15:39.58,italics,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Asta's always been full of energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.58,0:15:43.63,flashback,Father,0000,0000,0000,,This is Sister Lily. She'll be \Nworking here starting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.63,0:15:45.09,flashback,Father,0000,0000,0000,,All of you, be kind to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.09,0:15:49.97,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Wow... Sister Lily.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.97,0:15:51.26,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.26,0:15:54.26,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Please marry me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.72,0:15:58.22,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! I didn't mean to!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.22,0:16:00.31,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Lily...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.31,0:16:02.75,flashback,Rekka,0000,0000,0000,,He seems happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.23,0:16:08.07,italics,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,It might be because of Asta...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.57,0:16:10.74,italics,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,But Yuno's become so strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.62,0:16:19.99,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Asta...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.54,0:16:22.54,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,He's so beaten up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.67,0:16:25.12,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,It's all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.12,0:16:26.79,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,He was protecting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.32,0:16:28.32,flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.85,0:16:30.25,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno, you sound so...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.13,0:16:35.19,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Asta, stay with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.14,0:16:38.18,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Sister Lily...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.18,0:16:39.81,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Asta...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.81,0:16:42.68,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Please marry me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.68,0:16:44.18,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.19,0:16:48.97,italics,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.27,0:16:57.71,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It is summer. Asta and Yuno start their \Njourney to the royal capital in order to take
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.71,0:17:00.20,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,the Magic Knights Entrance Exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.45,0:17:05.71,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The royal capital is a long, \Nlong way from Hage Village.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.57,0:17:12.21,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,The royal capital, huh... I wonder what it's like.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.69,0:17:14.79,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if we'll get \Nto meet the Wizard King!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.79,0:17:17.93,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,First, we need to pass the \NMagic Knights entrance exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.93,0:17:19.34,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.34,0:17:20.72,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.17,0:17:23.98,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Excited? Aren't you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.32,0:17:26.06,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why would I be?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.26,0:17:28.57,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,You never change.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.57,0:17:31.62,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's hurry!\NThe royal capital's super far away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.62,0:17:32.44,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.44,0:17:34.99,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I've gotta hurry up and \Nbecome the Wizard King!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.53,0:17:37.37,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Just because you get there quickly
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.37,0:17:40.24,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,doesn't mean you'll become the \NWizard King any quicker.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.24,0:17:42.74,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the Wizard King, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.41,0:17:49.85,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,My, Asta, you look so impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.85,0:17:52.78,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Sister... no, my Lily.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.78,0:17:55.07,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I came for you, just as I promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.07,0:17:57.93,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I've become the Wizard King. Now, get on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.26,0:17:59.43,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.21,0:18:02.64,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.47,0:18:07.79,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It could happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.79,0:18:10.62,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Can you even ride a broom when \Nyou don't have any magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.73,0:18:13.54,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'll make it work!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.54,0:18:14.37,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.37,0:18:17.77,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I will! I got my grimoire!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.77,0:18:20.49,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I can do anything as long as I don't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.49,0:18:21.74,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.08,0:18:23.93,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna leave you behind, Yuno!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.93,0:18:26.67,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Let's train all the way to the royal capital!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.67,0:18:28.03,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.54,0:18:31.00,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Can't keep up, can you, Yuno?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.51,0:18:40.01,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not done yet... Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.75,0:18:47.34,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Stop. We've got a long way to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.94,0:18:51.74,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet! I'm not done yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.95,0:19:06.45,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hot! Hot, hot, hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.97,0:19:14.33,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I wish everyone back at the \Nchurch could eat this, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.33,0:19:15.47,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.81,0:19:19.97,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.43,0:19:25.98,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.98,0:19:27.47,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.62,0:19:45.70,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Stay out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.15,0:19:47.83,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I just gave you a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.83,0:19:49.57,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,No one asked you to!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.79,0:19:54.33,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.49,0:20:14.82,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,My precious moguro leaf juice!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.57,0:20:35.87,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Yuno?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.67,0:20:44.74,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, it's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.74,0:20:46.68,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So that's the royal capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.89,0:20:49.81,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That's where the Wizard King is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.19,0:20:57.55,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I'm gonna do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.55,0:21:01.42,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be right there! Just you wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.42,0:21:05.20,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the Wizard King!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.74,0:21:08.53,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,After a long and perilous journey,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.53,0:21:11.95,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Asta and Yuno arrive at the royal \Ncapital of the Clover Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.15,0:21:16.81,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The Magic Knights Entrance Exam awaits.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.51,0:21:24.43,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,They will now have to compete with many \Npowerful opponents and pass the exam!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.23,0:21:35.84,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,No one can escape from here
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.29,0:21:42.59,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Once again in the small closed off classroom
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.31,0:21:50.83,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The star of the class was shining yet again
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.43,0:21:57.28,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,They shine so bright that I close my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.27,0:22:00.71,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I've thought many times
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.03,0:22:04.42,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,That the revolution was within my hands
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.42,0:22:12.02,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it strange? If you want \Nto laugh, go ahead and laugh
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.02,0:22:18.85,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest of us who were left \Nbehind wanted to become something
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.16,0:22:26.11,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We repeat the same morning over and over
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.11,0:22:32.99,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one who \Ncan choose your tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.30,0:22:37.72,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go beyond our current selves
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.81,0:23:04.36,sign_33083_276_Petit_Clover_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,520)}Pe{\c&H3BC020&}t{\c&HE2AF0F&}i{\c&H3BC020&}t C{\c&HE2AF0F&}l{\c&H3BC020&}o{\c&H0E42D4&}ve{\c&H3BC020&}r
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.14,0:23:03.42,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Petit Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.86,0:23:07.86,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(523,1)}The Mystery of the Grimoire
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.22,0:23:06.99,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,The Mystery of the Grimoire!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.86,0:23:12.57,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what? We're small now?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.57,0:23:17.75,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,But man... Our grimoires \Nare totally different.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.27,0:23:19.29,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,He ignored me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.73,0:23:25.23,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,A grimoire's size and thickness are \Ndetermined by its owner's style.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.23,0:23:28.63,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Let's compare grimoires!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.63,0:23:29.60,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.63,0:23:31.51,sign_33774_286_That_thing_s_fil,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,That thing's\Nfilthy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.60,0:23:30.71,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,No fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.71,0:23:32.27,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You scared you're gonna lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.27,0:23:33.77,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Not a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.77,0:23:36.86,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You're getting a big head just because \Nyou're a little handsome, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.86,0:23:37.91,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Not a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.73,0:23:42.52,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,This is it, Yuno! The Magic Knights \Nwe admire so much are here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.52,0:23:46.11,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Our path to making our dream of becoming \Nthe Wizard King come true starts here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.11,0:23:50.78,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Black Clover,{\i0} Page 4:\N"The Magic Knights Entrance Exam!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.82,0:23:55.00,sign_34238_338_Page_2_The_Boys_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(234,1)}Page 4\N\N{\fs18}The Magic Knights Entrance Exam
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.78,0:23:53.70,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not giving up is my magic!
